      <title>中国人民银行潘基文称中国将于2月初下调银行存款准备金率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/pboc-s-pan-china-to-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行行长潘功胜表示，中国将在 2 月初降低银行存款准备金率，以释放更多资金并帮助经济。潘在北京举行的新闻发布会上宣布了这一消息。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/pboc-s-pan-china-to-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率判决前南非通胀处于四个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/south-africa-inflation-hits-four-month-low-before-rate-verdict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的通货膨胀率连续第二个月下降，这给央行在政策决定前夕提供了思考的空间，预计该政策将保持在 2009 年高位不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/south-africa-inflation-hits-four-month-low-before-rate-verdict</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于资产创历史新低，Abrdn 计划裁员 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/abrdn-plans-to-cut-10-of-workforce-as-assets-hit-record-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周三提交的文件，Abrdn Plc 计划裁减大约 500 个职位，即员工总数的 10%，作为每年节省至少 1.5 亿英镑（1.91 亿美元）计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/abrdn-plans-to-cut-10-of-workforce-as-assets-hit-record-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:44:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
